room_title: Escape room "Da Vinci's Secret" by Bust Out Escape Room in Albuquerque
room_address: 9440 San Mateo Blvd Suite K Albuquerque, NM 87113
room_description: Leonardo Da Vinci was one the greatest minds the world has ever known. He invented, painted, sculpted and did so many things that we are still trying to figure out. You have stumbled upon a secret room that appears to have been occupied by the great maestro. Use the clues and puzzles he has left for the worthy party that he knew someday would find his room.
